{"title":"英雄的开山工","authors":["李选吾"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的开山工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁路工人　李选吾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山工，谁不夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起铁锤走天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重重险峰任你踩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万丈山崖任你砸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩一锤，那热汗呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把崖上的冰雪冲刷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩两锤，那顽石呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞪着眼来肺气炸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩三锤，那笑脸呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看虎口把万吨炸药吞下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锤落炮声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西天呀，黑压压；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地震裂，山崩垮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火车云中走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不说高原风光最佳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山工，谁不夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起铁锤走天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命红旗高高举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏山崖，放眼亚非拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望越南，强盗在烧杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔仇恨火辣辣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抡起锤，你哪是在打眼呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是在打约翰逊的脑瓜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好哇，开山工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠狠揍，狠狠打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你八磅锤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把美国佬砸成豆腐渣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你开山炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把旧世界轰个流水落花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山工，谁不夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起铁锤走天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国叫声驱“穷白”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪儿艰苦哪儿去安家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峭壁上，把床架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢钎当睡枕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不疲乏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节日，登上峰顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望那天安门——放礼花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是“无限风光在险峰”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山美极啦！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}